Arguments

INPUT

raster - Gelaendemodell (DTM). Path to a raster layer.

INPUT2

raster - Hoehengradienten (Grad). Path to a raster layer.

INPUT10

raster - Flusseinzugsgebiet (BasinShare). Path to a raster layer.

INPUT8

raster - HG-Raster (HGGrid). Path to a raster layer.

INPUT9

raster - HG-Hoehengradienten (HGGrad). Path to a raster layer.

INPUT11

raster - Referenzverlauf Flussbilanz. Path to a raster layer.

INPUT12

raster - Zuflussrasterzellen (NumInFlowCells). Path to a raster layer.

INPUT3

raster - statische Wassserentnahme (statWUse). Path to a raster layer.

INPUT5

raster - Fluss-Speicher einlesen. Path to a raster layer.

INPUT6

raster - Oberflaechenabfluss-Speicher einlesen. Path to a raster layer.

INPUT7

raster - Grundwasserabfluss-Speicher einlesen. Path to a raster layer.

OUTPUT

rasterDestination - Fluss-Speicher ausgeben. Path for new raster layer.

OUTPUT2

rasterDestination - Oberflaechenabfluss-Speicher ausgeben. Path for new raster layer.

OUTPUT3

rasterDestination - Grundwasserabfluss-Speicher ausgeben. Path for new raster layer.

OUTPUT4

rasterDestination - Wasserflussvolumen. Path for new raster layer.

OUTPUT5

rasterDestination - SumRunoffDrainage. Path for new raster layer.

OUTPUT6

rasterDestination - DynWUse. Path for new raster layer.

onlyRB

boolean - Berechnung nur im Flusseinzugsgebiet. 1 for true/yes. 0 for false/no. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

TimeStep

number - Zeitschrittdauer (s). A numeric value. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

CalcT

boolean - automatisierter max. Zeitschritt. 1 for true/yes. 0 for false/no. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

sYear

number - Startjahr. A numeric value. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

DayNum

number - Anzahl der Simulationstage. A numeric value. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

Folder2

file - Speicherordner. Path to a file.

Folder1

file - Pfad LS-Daten. Path to a file.

stRedFacR

number - Reduzierungsfaktor Surface Runoff (% / 100). A numeric value. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

autoFacD

boolean - Ausgleich der Surface Runoff Reduktion. 1 for true/yes. 0 for false/no. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

stRedFacD

number - Reduzierungsfaktor Drainage (% / 100). A numeric value. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

OffsetR

number - Offsetwert Surface Runoff (m3/s). A numeric value. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

OffsetD

number - Offsetwert Drainage (m3/s). A numeric value. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

CacheUse

boolean - Initiierung mit vorhandenen Speichern. 1 for true/yes. 0 for false/no. field:FIELD_NAME to use a data defined value taken from the FIELD_NAME field. expression:SOME EXPRESSION to use a data defined value calculated using a custom QGIS expression.

Folder4

file - NCache einlesen. Path to a file.

wNC

logical specifying if complete out of qgisprocess::qgis_run_algorithm() should be used (TRUE) or first output (most likely the main) should read (FALSE). Default value is TRUE.
